reviewText: This is a great video. I had the Hands on Rigid Heddle Weaving book but couldn't figure out how to warp the loom. My husband got me this as a present. After watching the video, I was able to warp the loom. I was so thrilled!
this is NOT the fault of the seller BUT this video is awful. Very poor quality, poor camera shots and very poor content. I am VERY displeased.
